# Task 24 – Project Conclusion

## Project

Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This document summarizes the successful completion of the Smart Library Request Workflow project, highlighting objectives, implementation, achievements, testing, and future enhancements.

## Project Highlights

- Role-Based Access Control
- Book Management
- Borrow Request Workflow
- Flow Designer Automation
- UI Policies
- Access Control Lists (ACLs)
- Reference Qualifiers
- Email Notifications
- Reports and Dashboards
- End-to-End Testing

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- Flow Designer
- UI Policies
- Access Control Lists (ACLs)
- Reference Qualifiers
- Reports

## Outcome

The project successfully automated library borrowing and approval processes, improved operational efficiency, enhanced user experience, and established a scalable solution for future academic service automation.

## Status

Completed
